Title: The Brazilian
DateModified: '2019-02-15'
DatePublished: '2019-02-15'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-brazilian
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: clarissa ribeiro
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: Born in a little town in Brazil countiside in 1977 were the portuguese milionair
  Adriano Telles, owner of the A Brasileira (The Brazilian) caffee in Portugal lived,
  a girl travels to portugal to investigate the secrets behind the controversial and
  misterious events in Telles life that forced him to suddenly abandon his business
  in Brazil and move with the family back to Portugal leaving behind a ghost history
  and broken memories in Brazil.
